{"tid":607536,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費Sir涉23億鎊有組織逃稅案","createTime":"2018-03-27T11:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T05:09:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"27e0b3854ff06710c454a84028665ea5cc873308","tid":607536,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=7CbX9iiplNAojStizpFGOAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=e43f93c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西班牙逃稅風波蔓延到英格蘭，牽涉多名球壇中人，包括前曼聯領隊費格遜。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》周一報道，英國稅務海關總署最近正在調查一宗逃稅案，涉案人士利用政府對電影業嘅稅項優惠，假借投資之名，合共逃避了高達23億鎊稅項，而且是一個涉及780人的有組織逃稅計劃。<br />\n<br />\n780人當中，有不少是球壇中人，包括前曼聯領隊費格遜（Sir Alex Ferguson）、前英格蘭主帥荷杜、艾歷臣，以及紐卡素翼鋒蘇蘭奴、伯明翰左翼拿沙迪斯等多名前英超球員。英國退役球員福利組織Xpro證實，有多名前球員涉事，但他們辯稱不知道今次投資其實是逃稅。<br />\n<br />\n一經定罪，稅務海關總署將會向涉案人士收取懲罰性稅收，即應付稅項的20倍，屆時將令不少人無力清還而申請破產。"},{"pid":"51c86e1ce471dbb6d228794ef658a167ae94c508","tid":607536,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"Big害我獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5abb85d16e8e09d9ebc1abb53528bb0e0149f3a","tid":607536,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:26:10.000Z","msg":"仲以為係費天王，嚇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a16d2c858496814945970887784c5386de6eec","tid":607536,"uid":119778,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"呢個死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280d357e82c4ae41c1f4064afebdf6e682e5a7d2","tid":607536,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"罪成會唔會褫奪頭銜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b7d886564d1aa65dc8b8c241c285f6dd106769","tid":607536,"uid":37735,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyT